All Classes

Class Description
GatewayApplication
Main class for the SpringBoot based Web Application
HardwareUser
The HardwareUser object contains all the important user information for handling threads listening and sending information to the hardware
ISensorDataService
Sensor service interface
SensorDataController
The Sensor Controller handles the requests sent by the client (Data server)
SensorDataService
Implementation of the Sensor service interface
SensorEntry
SensorEntry object is the container for the data received from Loriot as an uplink and data to be sent to Loriot as a downlink
UserThreadFile
Persistence class used to store and update the list of user threads communicating to the Loriot server
WebSocketClient
WebSocket listener class used for the connection between the Gateway server and Loriot server
WebSocketThread
Runnable class used to manage the transmission of information between the socket client and the service classes
